headline: Mouser Electronics Named Global High Service Distributor of the Year by TE Connectivity for Eleventh Year
summary: DALLAS & FORT WORTH, Texas, July 22, 2025--Mouser Electronics, Inc., the authorized global distributor with the newest electronic components and industrial automation products, today announces it has received its eleventh Global High Service Distributor of the Year Award from TE Connectivity (TE), a world leader in connectivity and sensors. The prestigious distribution award recognizes Mouser's 2024 performance based on sales growth, market share growth, customer growth and business plan perform
